des:
Lamptan Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to control your devices！
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your device - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.

After connecting Alexa to your Lamptan Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Lamptan Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Lamptan Smart account in our "Lamptan Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Lamptan Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Lamptan Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Lamptan Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Lamptan Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Lamptan Smart", and you'll be navigated to Lamptan Smart login page;
(9). Input your Lamptan Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
